snippet.title: Super Cyborg - Steam Trailer [60fps]
snippet.description:
Super Cyborg is an 8-bit platformer shooter for PC, now available on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/341550

Basically this is an updated version of the old trailer, watch in 60FPS!

Visit my blog for updates: http://ar2rgames.blogspot.com 
music by Darkman007 http://darkman007.untergrund.net
